## LTM record formats

> 当前项目已停用 LTM。本规则仅供阅读 `ltm/` 历史文件时参考。

### events.jsonl

Each line: `{"id": "evt_NNNNNN", "ts": "ISO-8601", "type": "file_write|checkpoint|manual_note", ...}`

### checkpoints.jsonl

Each line: `{"id": "chk_NNNNNN", "ts": "ISO-8601", "summary": "text", "changed_files": [], ...}`

### Secret redaction

Check for: `sk_live_`, `sk_test_`, `AKIA`, `ghp_`, `gho_`, `-----BEGIN`, `Bearer`, base64 strings 40+ chars. Replace with `[REDACTED]`.
